砰然心动

李誉辉、张杰

2020年2月15日

1 简介

这里我们准备画个3D心型网格：

2 需要的包

library(dplyr)
library(tibble)
library(magrittr)
library(plot3D)
library(magick)
library(gganimate)
library(pracma)
library(purrr)

3 创建网格数据

x_y_z <- mesh(x = seq(-3, 3, len=101), 
              y = seq(-3, 3, len=101), 
              z = seq(-3, 3, len=101))

fun1 <- function(x, y, z){
  -x^2*z^3 - (9/80)*y^2*z^3 + 
    (x^2+(9/4)*y^2 + z^2 - 1)^3
}

arr1 <- with(x_y_z, fun1(x, y, z))
col1 <- rgb(1, 104/255, 181/255)

步长越小，contour越密。

iy <- seq(35, 67, by = 1) #
iz <- seq(41, 61, by = 6)
ix <- seq(36, 71, by = 6)

3.1 X-Z平面网格

3.1.1 等值线contour

for (i in 1:length(iy)){
  plane_y <- Reshape(arr1[,iy[i],], 101, 101)
  contour2D(plane_y)
  
}

3.1.2 单个contour

plane_y <- Reshape(arr1[,iy[length(iy)%/%2],], 101, 101)
contour_y <- contourLines(z = plane_y)[[1]] 
level_y <- contour_y$level
if (contour_y$level > 0){
  contour_df <- NA
} else {
  contour_df <- data.frame(x = (contour_y$x)*101, 
                           y = iy[2], 
                           z = (contour_y$y)*101)
}

with(contour_df,lines3D(x=x,y=y, z=z,lwd = 2,col="magenta"))

3.1.3 All of Contour

list_y <- list()
for (i in 1:length(iy)){
  plane_y <- Reshape(arr1[,iy[i],], 101, 101)
  contour_y <- contourLines(z = plane_y)[[1]] 
  level_y <- contour_y$level
  if (contour_y$level > 0){
    contour_df <- NA
  } else {
    contour_df <- data.frame(x = (contour_y$x)*101, 
                             y = iy[i], 
                             z = (contour_y$y)*101)
  }
  
  list_y[[i]] <- contour_df
  
}

# remove NA from list
list_y <- list_y[!is.na(list_y)]

3.1.4 Plot All of Contour

par(mar = c(0, 0, 0, 0))

perspbox(z=as.vector(0),xlim=c(40,72),ylim=c(40,72),zlim=c(40,72),
        ticktype = "detailed",bty = "g",box= TRUE,colkey = FALSE,
        theta = 27, phi = 15, d=3)
for (i in 1:length(list_y)){
  with(list_y[[i]],lines3D(x=x,y=y, z=z,lwd = 2,col="magenta",add=TRUE))
}

4 叠加contour

为了增加视觉美观性，
这里给一些contour填充白色,并设置完全不透明，
避免线条干扰。

# bind some list 
list_xz <- c(list_x, list_z) 
par(mar = c(0, 0, 0, 0))

perspbox(z=as.vector(0),xlim=c(40,72),ylim=c(40,72),zlim=c(40,72),
        ticktype = "detailed",bty = "g",box= FALSE,colkey = FALSE,
        theta = 27, phi = 15, d=3)

for (i in 1:length(list_xz)){
  with(list_xz[[i]],polygon3D(x=x,y=y, z=z, add=TRUE, 
                              col="white",lwd = 0.1,alpha=1))
  with(list_xz[[i]],lines3D(x=x,y=y, z=z, add=TRUE, 
                              col="magenta",lwd = 1,alpha=1))
}

for (i in 1:length(list_y)){
  with(list_y[[i]],lines3D(x=x,y=y, z=z,lwd = 2, 
                           col="magenta",add=TRUE))
}
